description:
Extend the BamlType derive macro to parse #[render(...)] attributes on structs and enums for type-level renderer registration.

Location: crates/baml-bridge-derive/src/lib.rs

Attribute syntax to support:
```rust
// Default Jinja template
#[render(default = r#"{{ value.field }}"#)]

// Named style with template
#[render(style = "compact", template = r#"..."#)]

// Named style with function
#[render(style = "debug", fn = "crate::render_debug")]

// Dynamic field access opt-in
#[render(allow_dynamic = true, template = "...")]
```

